  "text": "When women travelled to the clinic by foot or bicycle, we assumed zero travel costs. For women who travelled to the clinic by car, we assumed a mean distance to the clinic of 16.1 km at a cost of £0.28/km (AA Motoring costs, 2013; [CITATION_1] . Parking fees and costs of public transport/taxi were taken from the questionnaire directly.",
